<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>The Family Finance Reset</title>
  <meta name="description" content="A 90-day program for couples who earn good money but still feel broke. Build clarity, control, and a plan for your money." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --navy: #003366;
      --navy-dark: #002244;
      --lime: #99cc33;
      --bg: #f6f8fb;
      --text: #17202a;
      --muted: #5f6b7a;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --border: #d9e1ea;
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 32, 68, 0.12);
      --radius: 22px;
      --radius-sm: 14px;
      --max: 1180px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--bg);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

    .container {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      background: rgba(246, 248, 251, 0.82);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.08);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 16px 0;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .brand {
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--white);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.22);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--navy-dark); }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--navy);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 72px 0 50px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(153, 204, 51, 0.18), transparent 26%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f6f8fb 100%);
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 36px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(153, 204, 51, 0.14);
      color: var(--navy-dark);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 5vw, 4.3rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: var(--navy-dark);
    }

    .hero p.lead {
      font-size: 1.12rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 0 28px;
    }

    .hero-points {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin: 26px 0 32px;
    }

    .point {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--navy-dark);
    }

    .hero-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.08);
    }

    .video-wrap {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      padding-top: 56.25%;
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #0c1622;
    }

    .video-wrap iframe {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: 0;
    }

    .card-caption {
      padding: 14px 8px 4px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }

    section {
      padding: 72px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1.08;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--navy-dark);
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 0 32px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .problem-solution {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .panel {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 34px rgba(0, 32, 68, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.08);
    }

    .panel h3 {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      color: var(--navy-dark);
    }

    .list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .icon {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex: 0 0 28px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .icon.bad { background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.12); color: #a32133; }
    .icon.good { background: rgba(153, 204, 51, 0.18); color: #426d00; }

    .steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .step {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.08);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 32, 68, 0.07);
    }

    .step-number {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--white);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .step h4 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      color: var(--navy-dark);
    }

    .phase-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .phase {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f9fbff 100%);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 32, 68, 0.07);
    }

    .phase span {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .phase h4 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.24rem;
      color: var(--navy-dark);
    }

    .quote {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-dark), var(--navy));
      color: var(--white);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 34px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .quote p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
      line-height: 1.45;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .cta-box {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.08);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 36px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-box p {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 28px 0 56px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .problem-solution,
      .steps,
      .phase-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 48px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .container {
        width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 24px));
      }

      .nav {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .nav-links {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: space-between;
        overflow-x: auto;
        padding-bottom: 2px;
      }

      .hero-points {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .panel,
      .phase,
      .step,
      .cta-box,
      .quote {
        padding: 22px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.3rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="container nav">
      <a class="brand" href="#top">The Family Finance Reset</a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#problem">The Problem</a>
        <a href="#solution">The Solution</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a>
        <a href="#phases">What You Get</a>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#cta">Apply Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">90-Day Program for Couples</div>
          <h1>Earn good money.<br>Stop wondering where it all went.</h1>
          <p class="lead">The Family Finance Reset is for couples who should be doing well on paper, but still feel like the money disappears, the stress keeps building, and no one is fully in control.</p>
          <div class="hero-points">
            <div class="point">Build clarity around where your money is actually going</div>
            <div class="point">Stop the constant financial tension and guesswork</div>
            <div class="point">Create a realistic plan you can both stick to</div>
            <div class="point">Start making real progress toward savings and freedom</div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#cta">Book Your Reset</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#video">Watch The Overview</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-card" id="video">
          <div class="video-wrap">
            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9CYB5m2r-UU?si=LIJwpApo-UIfUh0y" title="YouTube video player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="card-caption">Watch the walkthrough to see how this 90-day reset helps couples go from reactive and messy to calm, aligned, and in control.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="problem">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">You’re not lazy. You’re just running without a clear system.</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">A lot of couples earn decent money and still feel behind. Not because they’re hopeless. Because they’ve never had a simple structure that actually works in real life.</p>
        <div class="problem-solution">
          <div class="panel">
            <h3>The Problem For Couples Like You</h3>
            <ul class="list">
              <li><span class="icon bad">✕</span><span>You make solid money, but it still feels like there’s never enough left over.</span></li>
              <li><span class="icon bad">✕</span><span>One or both of you avoid looking too closely because it feels overwhelming.</span></li>
              <li><span class="icon bad">✕</span><span>Spending is inconsistent, bills creep up, and savings goals keep getting pushed back.</span></li>
              <li><span class="icon bad">✕</span><span>Money conversations turn tense, vague, or repetitive instead of productive.</span></li>
              <li><span class="icon bad">✕</span><span>You know you should be further ahead by now, but you can’t seem to get traction.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="panel" id="solution">
            <h3>With The Family Finance Reset</h3>
            <ul class="list">
              <li><span class="icon good">✓</span><span>You’ll finally see exactly where your money is going each month.</span></li>
              <li><span class="icon good">✓</span><span>You’ll build a practical system that suits your real life, not some fake perfect budget.</span></li>
              <li><span class="icon good">✓</span><span>You’ll know what to cut, what to keep, and where to direct your money for progress.</span></li>
              <li><span class="icon good">✓</span><span>You’ll get on the same page as a couple and reduce the background stress.</span></li>
              <li><span class="icon good">✓</span><span>You’ll leave with more control, more confidence, and a clear path forward.</span></li>
              <li><span class="icon good">✓</span><span>No shame, no fluff, no financial jargon overload.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="how-it-works">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">How it works</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">This is a practical 90-day process designed to take you from confusion and inconsistency to clarity, alignment, and forward momentum.</p>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <h4>Audit what’s really happening</h4>
            <p>We map your income, spending, leaks, habits, and pressure points so you can see the truth clearly without the emotional fog.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <h4>Build your money system</h4>
            <p>We create a simple structure for bills, spending, saving, and financial decision-making that works for both people in the relationship.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <h4>Follow through with support</h4>
            <p>You implement the system over 90 days so this becomes your new normal, not another short burst of motivation that fades out.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="phases">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">What you’re getting</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">The reset is broken into clear stages so you’re not trying to fix everything at once.</p>
        <div class="phase-grid">
          <div class="phase">
            <span>Phase 1</span>
            <h4>Financial Clarity</h4>
            <p>Get clear on your income, fixed costs, variable spending, hidden leaks, and the patterns keeping you stuck.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="phase">
            <span>Phase 2</span>
            <h4>Couples Money System</h4>
            <p>Create a clear structure for cash flow, spending rules, savings priorities, and money conversations that actually work.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="phase">
            <span>Phase 3</span>
            <h4>90-Day Reset Implementation</h4>
            <p>Put the plan into motion with support, accountability, and simple next actions so you start seeing real progress fast.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="quote">
          <p>Most couples do not have an income problem. They have a clarity problem, a communication problem, and a system problem. Fix those, and everything starts moving.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="cta">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-box">
          <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 14px;">Ready to stop feeling broke on a good income?</h2>
          <p>This program is for couples who are done guessing, done drifting, and ready to build a calmer, cleaner, more intentional financial life together.</p>
          <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:your@email.com?subject=Family%20Finance%20Reset%20Application">Apply Now</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#top">Back to Top</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">© The Family Finance Reset. Replace the apply button link, email address, and any copy you want to tighten before going live.</div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
